<collectingCountry id="BC83766EFFC56A7AFE3B9A1D1C56B76F" box="[455,598,3140,3165]" name="Zimbabwe" pageId="62" pageNumber="820">Zimbabwe</collectingCountry>
in Mana Pools National Park; it may occur in 
<collectingCountry id="BC83766EFFC56A7AFB0F9A1D1EFCB7B4" name="Mozambique" pageId="62" pageNumber="820">Mozambique</collectingCountry>
