<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFFC56A7AFA5994A61814B82E" bold="true" box="[1445,1556,767,796]" pageId="62" pageNumber="820">Habitat.</emphasis>
Woodlands and riverine forests.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FFC56A7AFA599578168CB858" pageId="62" pageNumber="820" type="food_feeding">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFFC56A7AFA599578168CB858" blockId="62.[1444,2652,289,1153]" pageId="62" pageNumber="820">
<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFFC56A7AFA59957818A7B870" bold="true" box="[1445,1703,801,834]" pageId="62" pageNumber="820">Food and Feeding.</emphasis>
